  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the unaccompanied refugee minors on Lesvos</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Better Days Greece provides a full emergency protection program for the most vulnerable children of the refugee community. We operate in Moria refugee camp, focusing on identifying, tracking and registering unaccompanied minors who have arrived and are cut off from support. Our program finds, registers and supports them with their basic needs through providing emergency aid packs, critical legal support, access to shelter, education, and psychosocial &amp; resilience support.</narrative>
  </description>
